        <b>Max Damage:</b> 197.75<br>
        <b>Damage/Delay Ratio:</b> Insane (0.875)<br>
        <b>Max Attack Speed:</b> A Bit Slow (22.222)<br>
        <b>Weapon Performance:</b> Amazing (13.912)<br>
<b>Effect Details:</b>&nbsp; This proc damages the target by 150 hitpoints as well as stunning them interrupting any casting the target may be doing.  It is fire based, which makes the proc more useful in many situations than the magic based procs of most weapons.<br>
